20:07.500 --> 20:08.592
That's why
you married him?

20:08.640 --> 20:10.767
Not for any tax
or health benefit,

20:10.810 --> 20:12.300
but because
you loved him?

20:12.340 --> 20:13.329
DALE:
Yes.

20:13.380 --> 20:14.369
Shakespeare said,

20:14.410 --> 20:16.002
"A man in hue,

20:16.040 --> 20:18.543
_all 'hues'_in
his controlling."

20:19.580 --> 20:20.945
