21:06.990 --> 21:10.562
Wait. Maybe that's not
what you meant.

21:10.600 --> 21:12.989
Who are you dating
on these date nights?

21:15.040 --> 21:17.634
BUCKY:
Mr. Lamborne?

21:17.670 --> 21:18.932
Other people.

21:18.970 --> 21:20.972
BUCKY:
Ah, I see.
So Free Fridays

21:21.010 --> 21:23.035
