you allow your spouse

21:23.080 --> 21:25.640
and your spouse allows you
to have sex

21:25.680 --> 21:27.568
with other men?

21:27.620 --> 21:30.043
(sighs)

21:30.080 --> 21:32.719
Mr. Lamborne,

21:32.750 --> 21:35.310
you must answer.

21:35.360 --> 21:37.920
