to show equivalence.

22:15.460 --> 22:20.124
Mr. Foster, please
excuse our impertinence.

22:20.170 --> 22:22.138
How many affairs
have you had?

22:22.170 --> 22:24.058
Oh.

22:24.110 --> 22:26.908
Mr. Foster, it is now
an issue of fact.

22:26.940 --> 22:28.532
Please answer.

22:28.580 --> 22:29.706
(sighs)

22:29.740 --> 22:32.004
Five affairs.

22:32.050 --> 22:33.642
BRESLOW (laughing):
Oh, come.

22:33.680 --> 22:35.113
Remind him
he's under oath.

22:35.150 --> 22:36.845
We have a record of 12.

22:36.880 --> 22:38.848
Okay. Enough.
Thank you.

22:38.890 --> 22:39.914
I'm ready to rule.

22:39.950 --> 22:42.111
It is true

22:42.160 --> 22:44.025
that the courts have been
allowed leeway

22:44.060 --> 22:48.394
to discern whether individual
marriages are legitimate,

22:48.430 --> 22:50.864
but I find the facts here

22:50.900 --> 22:52.822
to suggest nothing more
than equivalence.

22:52.870 --> 22:54.167
Some

22:54.200 --> 22:57.408
heterosexual marriages
are... messy.

22:57.440 --> 22:59.704
