34:34.540 --> 34:36.394
Well, basically What she says
is that our obsession

34:36.440 --> 34:38.635
with the clitoris
is unhealthy, 'cause...
Mom.

34:38.670 --> 34:40.809
Oh. Hi.
I was just telling Will

34:40.840 --> 34:43.206
about the vagina book
we're reading.
I'm not

34:43.240 --> 34:44.400
reading it.
No, it sounds interesting.

34:44.450 --> 34:45.803
VERONICA: Well,
I'll get you a copy.

34:45.850 --> 34:47.147
You're really not
seeing anyone?

34:47.180 --> 34:48.477
I'm really not
seeing anyone.

34:48.520 --> 34:49.771
Okay, Mom,
right this way.

34:49.820 --> 34:51.185
Talk to you later.
(mouthing)

34:51.220 --> 34:52.778
VERONICA:
I'm getting you that book!

34:52.820 --> 34:55.812
MAN: Shall
we get started,
Mr. Cavanaugh?

34:55.860 --> 34:56.713
Yes, okay.

34:56.760 --> 34:59.479
My client claims
he discussed an affair

34:59.530 --> 35:01.794
between your mother
and another man.

35:01.830 --> 35:03.127
Isn't that true?

35:06.470 --> 35:07.892
No, it's not.

35:07.930 --> 35:09.795
You Hear!
Restrain
your client.

35:09.840 --> 35:10.590
He's the one
who lied.

35:10.640 --> 35:12.699
He's the one who got
the will amended

35:12.740 --> 35:13.900
so that he
could cheat

35:13.940 --> 35:16.170
