of her property.

35:16.210 --> 35:18.678
(two lawyers speaking at once)

35:21.280 --> 35:23.919
(two lawyers continue arguing)

35:23.950 --> 35:27.442
There were two
Wiretaps, Buclq.

35:27.490 --> 35:29.583
And that should
impress me Why?

35:29.620 --> 35:31.656
Your key witness,
Vance Foster,

35:31.690 --> 35:33.328
he was being
investigated

35:33.360 --> 35:35.328
by State on
embezzlement
charges.

35:35.360 --> 35:37.157
Are you involved
with this?

35:37.200 --> 35:38.269
Involved with what?

35:38.300 --> 35:40.188
Keeping things from
your cocounsel, Ms. Lockhart?

35:40.230 --> 35:42.289
We subpoenaed
a second Wiretap from State.

35:42.340 --> 35:44.365
It gives a clearer picture
of Foster.

35:44.410 --> 35:46.469
DIANE: He bought a yacht--
he admits it in the call

35:46.510 --> 35:47.465
with his mistress.

35:47.510 --> 35:49.239
The yacht came from a kickback

35:49.280 --> 35:50.633
on the fraudulent tax returns.

35:52.210 --> 35:54.178
I'll get back to you.

35:54.220 --> 35:55.448
